  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Haunting Eyes</strong> is a game that takes you to a mansion where a tragic event, known only to you, took place 20 years ago. You, Daniel, are the best friend of a girl who died at the hands of her husband. Daniel agrees to his last certain case and arrives there, but who knows what secrets this mansion hides? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the mansion.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/9226febfd3e260bdcdf184a1e8647dad.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beware! This old and forgotten place has become a nightmare for every person who comes here. Old corridors, howling wind on the floors, creaking doors and distant screams. Wander through the mansion and learn its history. What does this place hide within itself?</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Try to survive among the ghost.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/51dc360b9a993596076eb1ee19c345c2.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"..Be quiet! I think.. it's already here! It's coming for you... for revenge..\"</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immerse yourself in the full story with beautiful cut-scenes.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/fb0e8f52d3611ad8767fe7350e631fde.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out what happened to Daniel! What lurks in this scary and forgotten mansion? What's keeping everyone from living their lives in peace?</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/9bd6f47e2871d7658b5205482393bc70.avif?t=1741208873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras_big/9bd6f47e2871d7658b5205482393bc70.avif?t=1741208873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
